{"tid":668390,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Oracle揭Google大量收集Android用戶定位數據　澳洲政府展開調查","createTime":"2018-05-17T14:45:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-18T04:40:36.000Z","uid":1886,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"b552d8c35742877dc971ef0792d0dfd0b09eecfc","tid":668390,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T14:45:15.000Z","msg":"澳洲傳媒周一（14日）報道，軟件公司甲骨文（Oracle）指Google涉嫌大量收集Android手機用戶的相關數據，包括詳細地點資訊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，估計每年收集的數據總值高達5.8億澳元（約34億港元）。澳洲競爭與消費者事務委員會（Australian Competition and Consumer Commission）就此展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1445575/org/c6e3b4423e33d5572b93e92bf7426083.jpg/6ZwLXQqd4gx4R8s_PDX3DPVVfcWoVIIUjqGa3o6hmt4?v=w1600r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1445575%2Forg%2Fc6e3b4423e33d5572b93e92bf7426083.jpg%2F6ZwLXQqd4gx4R8s_PDX3DPVVfcWoVIIUjqGa3o6hmt4%3Fv%3Dw1600r16_9&h=0cd78b4e&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n甲骨文公司代表向澳洲競爭與消費者事務委員會指出，Google涉嫌大量收集Android手機用戶的相關數據，包括搜尋和瀏覽記錄。即使用戶關閉定位服務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，甚至沒有安裝SIM卡或有關手機應用程式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，Android裝置均會發送出準確的地點資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。Google已標示出IP地址<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 、WiFi連接點和手機信號塔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，可藉此得知裝置位置<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，因此用戶可謂避無可避<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲現時有1000萬Android手機用戶。按當地每月1G數據收費3.6至4.5澳元估算，Google每年收集的數據總值高達5.8億澳元<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲隱私基金會（Australian Privacy Foundation）主席韋爾（David Vaile）指出，Google的原意是希望令公司的地圖街景服務變得更精確，但現時卻利用此功能大量收集數據<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。他更指，Google和Facebook一樣，均從事商業監控<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/188335/oracle%E6%8F%ADgoogle%E5%A4%A7%E9%87%8F%E6%94%B6%E9%9B%86android%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B6%E5%AE%9A%E4%BD%8D%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A-%E6%BE%B3%E6%B4%B2%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%B1%95%E9%96%8B%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2F188335%2Foracle%25E6%258F%25ADgoogle%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2587%258F%25E6%2594%25B6%25E9%259B%2586android%25E7%2594%25A8%25E6%2588%25B6%25E5%25AE%259A%25E4%25BD%258D%25E6%2595%25B8%25E6%2593%259A-%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E5%25B1%2595%25E9%2596%258B%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5&d=CjZ%2F%2FeBCvDBHkUoqNCXKLi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=d15f31ca\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/188335/oracle%E6%8F%ADgoogle%E5%A4%A7%E9%87%8F%E6%94%B6%E9%9B%86android%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B6%E5%AE%9A%E4%BD%8D%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A-%E6%BE%B3%E6%B4%B2%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%B1%95%E9%96%8B%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5</a>"},{"pid":"f6908ef2905eee54b460cc01d3b217620cdc6dbf","tid":668390,"uid":1886,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T14:46:03.000Z","msg":"Google指出，收集數據事前得到用戶同意。按公司隱私政策列明，當用戶使用Google服務時，Google有權獲取有關的IP地址和地點等資訊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。Google私隱處理同意書（Privacy Concent）列明，當家使Google Maps搜尋一定餐廳時， Google會追蹤用家所在位置。但內文看來沒有提及，當Google Maps不在使用之時，它仍會監控數據<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\nGoogle發言人拒絕就媒體特定提問回應，但稱用家可在「我的帳戶」（My Account）看到自己有什麼數據被收集，以及選擇是否跟Google分享所在地定位。"},{"pid":"60573dc5db1d6cd889f013d9a6e11151cbc0fd6b","tid":668390,"uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T14:49:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/business/breakingnews/2426509\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbusiness%2Fbreakingnews%2F2426509&d=CjZ%2F%2FeBCvDBHkUoqNCXKLi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=f3fe7b08\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbusiness%2Fbreakingnews%2F2426509&h=d6cd13d9\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/business/breakingnews/2426509</a><br />\n<br />\n根據澳州報社報導，甲骨文稱Google利用安卓系統蒐集如搜尋紀錄、所在地點等詳細資料，並傳回資料庫，這些數據在用戶不知情下傳輸，流量大小以GB計算。澳州隱私權基金會董事法爾（David Vaile）表示：「有些民眾的資費方案只有幾GB的上限，對他們來說，Google就算只偷用了1GB的流量都損失慘重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。」<br />\n<br />\n而Google發言人則回應，都有經過用戶的同意才蒐集資料。分析師估計澳州約有1000萬安卓用戶，但多數人在註冊服務時可能根本不了解使用規範的內容。澳洲最大電信商Telstra表示：「我們有注意到此消息，並已詢問Google消息內容是否正確。」"},{"pid":"2784e8c64a7650d9b8d86ae4c68728743339b663","tid":668390,"uid":106027,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T14:50:46.000Z","msg":"<del>軟件</del>法務公司甲骨文"},{"pid":"e99e4d0f70a3383801a3395eb39083aea0524dad","tid":668390,"uid":12628,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T15:40:54.000Z","msg":"開心大發現"},{"pid":"6c038a77cf84353e1af3ec2f2552f2ee39743fcc","tid":668390,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T15:41:51.000Z","msg":"期望wp 翻身"},{"pid":"087f780aecec0f7af2c95e7b83d4d33b1630bdd0","tid":668390,"uid":45285,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T15:45:05.000Z","msg":"其實oracle對業界有乜貢獻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上庭多過攪業界event <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fabc658ad6efe0